# Company: Configu

- Website: https://configu.com
- Founder(s): Peleg Porat
- Location: Israel
- Primary Category: Developer Tools

## What they do
Configu helps teams manage and validate configuration files at scale.

## Target user (ICP)
Developers, DevOps engineers managing complex configs.

## Key features
- Config validation
- Schema enforcement
- Config drift prevention

## Pricing
Free + paid tiers

## Positioning
“Configuration done right.”

## Overlap with Clode
- Improves reliability of deployment workflows

## How Clode is different
- Clode automates full cloud operations, not just configs

## DevRel angle
Position Clode as operating beyond config correctness.

## Content hooks
1. Config problems are symptoms, not root causes
2. Automation should reduce decision fatigue
